Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.82,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.41,0:12:20.50,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,是我幹的
