Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.08,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.16,0:12:47.98,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,阿蘭
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,阿蘭
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.42,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,阿蘭
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.99,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的花
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.99,0:13:00.03,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.97,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這叫留聲三角梅
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.40,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,貼膠帶是為甚麼
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.93,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這個啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.93,0:13:09.42,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這是種植留聲三角梅時不可或缺的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.24,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,因為啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.94,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,雖然美麗但也是恐怖的花
