Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,真是煩得要死
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.28,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,報復
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.95,0:15:44.69,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,阿忍
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.82,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這花是
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.51,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,阿當也有嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.07,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這根本拔不掉啊
