Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.79,0:16:58.96,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,一蹶不振
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.96,0:17:00.00,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,把老師
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.00,0:17:00.93,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,報復
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.12,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,一蹶不振
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.36,0:17:09.96,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,果然週日不太好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.97,0:17:16.86,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,就算上學用的直升機故障
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.53,0:17:18.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,就不能
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.00,0:17:21.53,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,準備點像樣的交通工具嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.53,0:17:24.73,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,覺得著如此風雅也不錯
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,風雅嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.05,0:17:32.46,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這不是阿忍嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.07,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,哎呀 是面堂君
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.97,0:17:38.04,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,面堂君居然也遲到真少見啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.04,0:17:40.33,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,見笑了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.73,0:17:42.08,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,其實今天
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.78,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,尿床了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.97,0:17:49.36,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,面堂
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.14,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,再說一遍
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.41,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,為甚麼遲到了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.56,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不是說
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.56,0:17:57.10,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,尿床了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.39,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,尿床了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.10,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這甚麼花
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.37,0:18:03.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,尿床了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.66,0:18:05.52,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,阿忍 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.93,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,冷靜一下
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.93,0:18:07.88,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這花擅自
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.88,0:18:08.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.66,0:18:10.07,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不要解釋了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.72,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,諸星你
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.05,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,尿床了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.34,0:18:14.66,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,希望你別說了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.02,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,你知道吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.52,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,是花在說
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.52,0:18:18.70,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,別隱瞞了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.28,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,現在的問題不是花
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.21,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,是你尿床
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.21,0:18:24.75,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.85,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,尿床了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.29,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,都說沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.31,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,尿床了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.31,0:18:32.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,尿了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.05,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,都那麼大了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.05,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,尿床了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.98,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,都回收那麼多了沒問題了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.29,0:18:46.79,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,還好沒鬧大
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.69,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,可喜可賀
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.40,0:18:51.16,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,開門啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.16,0:18:54.53,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,特意週日把人叫來這甚麼意思
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.89,0:18:59.99,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我知道你們的企圖
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.99,0:19:01.19,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,一蹶不振
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.45,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,把老師
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.45,0:19:10.09,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,報復  一蹶不振
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.09,0:19:11.63,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,都說了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.95,0:19:13.20,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,尿床了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.56,0:19:16.01,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,別過來 尿床小鬼
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.99,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,太受打擊了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.43,0:19:20.31,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.71,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,尿床了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.15,0:21:09.74,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,又累又餓
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.96,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不能氣餒
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.07,0:21:18.97,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.34,0:21:23.64,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.64,0:21:27.31,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,好不容易炸的天婦羅要涼了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.15,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,這樣的話咱倆
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,老師好慢啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.57,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,都準備晚餐了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.57,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,我忍不了了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.57,0:21:38.50,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.50,0:21:39.41,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.56,0:21:43.59,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,上門推銷天婦羅真是聞所未聞
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.17,0:21:44.92,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,天婦羅的香味
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.18,0:21:47.87,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,餓了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.50,0:21:51.83,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.43,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,聽到甚麼了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.67,0:21:55.78,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不是電視嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.67,0:21:56.51,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.51,0:21:59.19,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,要來點美味天婦羅嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.45,0:22:01.38,Dial_CH2,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.97,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.97,0:22:04.47,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,老師這份剩下了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.75,0:22:06.88,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,留著可惜了 都吃了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.65,0:22:11.98,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,飽了飽了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.98,0:22:15.43,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,要是不來說一聲多好
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.42,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,他就是不負責的傢伙
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.27,0:22:26.33,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,就不該做家訪的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.57,0:22:47.27,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,下集福星小子
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.27,0:22:49.37,Dial_CH,,0,0,0,,不是狐狸 是阿忍
